body: I missed my bus stop and had to walk back home
Missed my bus stop again! I think this time it was the bus driver’s mistake.
I think this was the time the bus didn’t come so I walked to the next stop.
This was the bus trip where the driver got a bit lost. The trip took and extra 40 minutes.

We picked up Erika and took her to a surprise 90th birthday party at the Gap Tavern. Everyone came to Erika's great surprise. She said this was the biggest surprise of her whole life!

We had a special closed-off and air-conditioned area on the verandah for the party. It was a very hot and humid day so it was good to be in there. The children's play room was really hot even with the windows and door open - probably because of all the video games in the small room.
I think this was the farewell party for Mary O’Neill who retired. Anita dropped me off and I caught a bus home afterwards.
